title: Harvest Moon Deli
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small, locally owned deli with numerous vegetarian and vegan options. The sandwiches are named after famous musicians. Offers both tempeh and veggie burger as vegan protein options, hummus and other spreads, as well as a variety of vegetables in the build your own sandwich category. Also has soups and salads as well as snacky items such as local herbal popcorn, chips, and both vegetarian and vegan packaged cookies. Sources local ingredients.
